title: Pink Floyd: The Endless River (2014) [FLAC]
description:
Dedicated as a "swan song" for Wright, The Endless River is mostly an instrumental album consisting primarily of ambient music. The album is based on unreleased material the band produced with Wright during sessions for The Division Bell in 1994, and was originally recorded under the tentative title The Big Spliff. Enjoy...

1. Morning's Kiss [2:46]
2. Nighttime Skyline [4:28]
3. Grassy Horizons [2:36]
4. The Days of Yore [5:40]
5. Troubled Waters [5:44]
6. The Wise Vagabond [25:06]
